Re: Translation Help
by AJBryant » Sun 07.31.2011 11:42 pm It should probably be pointed out, as well, that there is no such thing as "THE bushido code." Those are just random values someone thought sounded good. There isn't ANY bushido code -- nothing codified, anyway.
http://www.sengokudaimyo.com
